img=\"443\" img_width=\"107\" pos=\"right\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.1\" font_size__sm=\"1\"]\n\n<h3>Tri nghim m thc ngon ming</h3>\r\nTo ra nhng ba n vi hng v tuyt vi  khch hng c th thng thc nhng ba n ngon hng ngy.\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\" animate=\"fadeInRight\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"444\" img_width=\"107\" pos=\"left\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.1\" font_size__sm=\"1\"]\n\n<h3>An ton v dinh dng</h3>\r\nTun th nghim ngt cc tiu chun v an ton thc phm, m bo rng mi khu phn n u an ton, b dng v lnh mnh.\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\" animate=\"fadeInLeft\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"445\" img_width=\"107\" pos=\"right\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.1\" font_size__sm=\"1\"]\n\n<h3>Tin li cho cuc sng bn rn</h3>\r\nMang n s tin li, p ng nhu cu khch hng c th tn hng ba n ngon m khng lo lng v vic chun b.\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\" animate=\"fadeInRight\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"446\" img_width=\"107\" pos=\"left\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.1\" font_size__sm=\"1\"]\n\n<h3>Cht lng v quy trnh bi bn</h3>\r\nTp trung vo vic duy tr cht lng v quy trnh sn xut bi bn  m bo s pht trin bn vng v s hi lng ca khch hng.\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]\n[section bg=\"347\" bg_size=\"original\" bg_overlay=\"rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.756)\" bg_pos=\"48% 68%\" parallax=\"7\" padding=\"79px\"]\n\n[row h_align=\"center\"]\n\n[col span=\"7\" span__sm=\"12\" padding__sm=\"0px 50px 0px 15px\" animate=\"fadeInLeft\" class=\"pd-0\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.3\" text_align=\"center\" text_color=\"rgb(255,255,255)\"]\n\n<h3>ng k ngay  nhn thng tin nhng quyn thng hiu</h3>\n[/ux_text]\n[contact-form-7 id=\"349\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]\n[section bg_color=\"rgb(255, 246, 252)\" padding=\"80px\"]\n\n[row]\n\n[col span__sm=\"12\" animate=\"fadeInLeft\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.4\" font_size__sm=\"1.3\"]\n\n<h2 class=\"uppercase lts-04