 sng thng khin bn cm thy i hn v d dng la chn nhng mn n khng lnh mnh hoc n vt nhiu hn.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>nh Hng n Tm Trng:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> B qua ba sng c th gy ra cm gic mt mi, kch ng v nh hng tiu cc n tm trng.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Ri Lon Metabolism: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vic khng n sng lm chm qu trnh trao i cht, gy kh khn trong vic kim sot cn nng v c th gy mt cn bng lng ng trong mu.</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Tng Nguy C Mc Bnh: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B ba sng c th lm tng nguy c mc cc bnh nh tiu ng v bnh tim mch.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nhng la chn ba sng dinh dng lnh mnh</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong bi cnh cuc sng hin i ngy cng bn rn, vic tm kim mt ba sng nhanh chng nhng vn y  dinh dng l iu khng h n gin. y l l do ti sao</span><b> Cm Tm</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> tr thnh s la chn l tng cho bt k ai ang tm kim mt ba sng dinh dng lnh mnh.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ti Cm Tm, chng ti cung cp cc mn n sng lnh mnh, p ng mi nhu cu khu v. Mi mn n c chun b t nguyn liu ti ngon v cht lng cao, mang n hng v mm ngon - b dng  bt u mt ngy mi trn y nng lng.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">n vi Cm Tm, bn c th yn tm rng mi la chn ba sng l s kt hp hon ho gia v ngon v s lnh mnh - mt bc khi u l tng cho mt ngy mi y sc sng v hiu qu.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Kt:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Nh vy,<strong> ba sng</strong> khng ch khi u ngy mi, m cn l nn tng vng chc cho sc khe ca chng ta. Hy vng qua bi vit ny, chng ta ng xem nh ba sng - hy coi n nh l bc u tin trong hnh trnh hng ti mt ngy lm vic y nng lng v mt cuc sng khe mnh.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;", "Ti Sao Ba Sng Li L Ba n Quan Trng Nht Trong Ngy?", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "288-revision-v1", "", "", "2023-12-16 14:46:11", "2023-12-16 07:46:11", "", "288", "http://comtim.vn/?p=291", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `h7E2w_posts` VALUES("292", "1", "2023-12-16 14:53:22", "2023-12-16 07:53:22", "<em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">iu g to nn mt<strong> ba n cn i</strong> v lm th no  chng ta c th t c iu ny mi ngy? Bi vit ny s gip bn gii p cu hi trn v mang n thng tin hu ch  bn c th t to nn nhng ba n cn i, giu dinh dng cho bn thn v gia nh.</span></em>\r\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ba n nh th no l cn i v  cht?</span></h1>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mt ba n cn i v y  dinh dng cn p ng cc tiu ch chnh sau: khu phn bt ng chim khong 65 - 70%, cht m chim 12 - 14%, v cht bo chim 18 - 20% tng lng nng lng tiu th. y l c s  m bo sc khe v tui th ca mi ngi.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ngoi ra, bn khng th b qua vic b sung thm cc khong cht, vitamin v nc cho c th t rau, tri cy,... iu ny khng ch tng cng sc khe tng th m cn cn i v ngun thc n t c ng vt v thc vt trong khu phn n hng ngy.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mi ngi nn xy dng cho mnh mt ch  n ung ph hp vi khu v v iu kin thc phm sn c. Vic phn b nng lng cho cc ba n trong ngy cng quan trng. T l khuyn ngh l 30% cho ba sng, 40% cho ba tra, 25% cho ba ti v 5% dnh cho ba ph.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> t c ba n cn i v  cht, vic phn b cht dinh dng cn tun theo t l: cht bt ng chim 60%, cht m 15%, cht bo 25%, v cht x khong 30g mi ngy. S cn nhc v la chn thng minh trong vic xy dng ba n s ng gp ln vo vic duy tr mt li sng khe mnh.</span>\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_294\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"604\"]<img class=\"wp-image-294 size-full\" src=\"http://comtim.vn/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/images-com-tim-post-desc-07.jpg\" alt=\"Ba n nh th no l cn i v  cht?\" width=\"604\" height=\"593\" /> Ba n nh th no l cn i v  cht?[/caption]\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nhng nhm cht cn thit trong thc n n ung</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi xy dng mt ba n cn i, vic hiu r v tch hp  cc nhm cht dinh dng cn thit l v cng quan trng. Mt thc n n ung lnh mnh nn bao gm cc nhm cht sau:</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nhm bt ng</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nhm ny l ngun cung cp nng lng chnh cho mi hot ng ca c th. Go c xem l ngun lng thc chnh trong mi ba n hng ngy. Bn nn u tin s dng go lt  m bo y  cht dinh dng, h tr gim nguy c tiu ng v gip kim sot ng huyt trong mu. Cc loi thc phm bt ng khc nh khoai lang, ng, khoai ty,... cng nn c a vo thc n hng ngy  a dng ha ngun nng lng cho c th.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nhm cht m</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Protein cn thit cho c th tng trng, tng cng sc  khng, phc hi c bp cng nh cc chc nng sinh hc khc.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Protein t cc thc phm ng vt nh tht, c, sa, trng v m thc vt t u, ,... l cha kha cho s pht trin v sc  khng ca c th. S cn nhc gia tht  v tht gia cm, cng vi vic b sung cc loi c cha Omega-3, gip cn bng lng m tiu th.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nhm cht bo</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cht bo lnh mnh t du thc vt v m ng vt, c bit l ngun omega-3 t m c gip cung cp nng lng v h tr hp th vitamin. Chng gip tng cng sc khe tim mch v duy tr cn nng khe mnh. Ngi tiu dng nn u tin du thc vt cha cht bo khng bo ha v hn ch tiu th m ng vt.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nhm vitamin v khong cht</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cht x khng ch gip tiu ha d dng m cn h tr kim sot lng ng trong mu. Mt ch  n giu cht x t rau c v tri cy s l bn ng hnh khng th thiu trong mi ba n.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rau c qu l ngun cung cp vitamin v khong cht v cng phong ph. Mi ngi nn tiu th t nht 400g rau c qu mi ngy  m bo sc khe ti u, c bit l nhng loi rau c l mu xanh m v c qu mu vng,  giu vitamin A v st.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nguyn tc xy dng ba n cn i</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> duy tr sc khe tt v cn nng hp l, vic xy dng ba n cn i theo nguyn tc dinh dng v khoa hc l v cng quan trng. Mi ba n trong ngy cn c cn nhc k lng v thnh phn v lng thc n, t ba sng, tra, cho n ba ti.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ba sng - Khi u nng lng</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ba sng c xem l ba n quan trng nht trong ngy. V th, nn m bo cung cp  cc nhm thc phm bao gm bt m (nh bnh m, cm, ph), cht m (tht, c, trng, sa), cht bo (b, du n) v vitamin cng mui khong t rau c qu.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lu : Tp trung vo vic b sung cht m  kch thch hot ng ca no b v duy tr s linh hot, mnh khe.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ba tra - B sung nng lng</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ba tra cn cung cp nhiu nng lng cho c th vi s cn i ca tinh bt, cht x v cht m.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lu : Khuyn khch b sung c vo ba tra v n cung cp nhiu dng cht quan trng v rau, c, qu l thc phm khng th thiu.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ba ti - n nh, n ng</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hn ch n qu no vo ba ti  trnh p sut ln d dy tng cao v nguy c tch t nng lng tha dn n bo ph.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lu : Nn n ng gi v la chn cc loi thc phm nh nhng, d tiu ha.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nhng lu  khi xy dng ch  n ung</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> xy dng ba n cn i khng ch l la chn thc phm ph hp m cn cn tun theo nhng nguyn tc c bn. Di y l mt s lu  quan trng m bn cn ghi nh khi xy dng ch  n ung ca mnh:</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">n ung ng cch bng cch gim lng mui trong ch  n: n tha mui c th gy ra nhiu vn  sc khe nh tng huyt p v nguy c bnh tim. Hy hn ch lng mui tiu th hng ngy xung ch cn khong 5g, trnh xa cc loi thc phm cha nhiu mui nh gi, ch, tht xng khi, v thc phm ch bin sn.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ung  nc v hn ch ru bia: m bo ung  1.5 - 2 lt nc mi ngy, nht l trong nhng ngy nng nng. Hn ch ung ru bia, khng nn ung qu 2 cc bia hoc 2 chn ru 30ml cho nam gii v  liu lng  cho n gii mi ngy.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">iu chnh dinh dng ph hp vi mi la tui: Mi la tui c nhu cu dinh dng ring.Tr em cn thc n d nhai v nut, trong khi tr sau 6 thng tui v ngi trng thnh nn c b sung sa v cc ch phm t sa  tng cng hp th cht m v canxi.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>Kt: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Qua bi vit m Cm Tm  chia s, hi vng bn  c ci nhn r rng v ton din v cch to nn mt ba n cn i v  dinh dng. Hy </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">nh rng, mi la chn thc phm, mi s kt hp trn a n, khng ch l vic nui dng c th m cn l vic chm sc sc khe ca bn v gia nh.</span>", "Lm Th No  To Nn Ba n Cn i V y  Dinh Dng?", "", "publish", "open", "open", "", "lam-the-nao-de-tao-nen-bua-an-can-doi-va-day-du-dinh-duong", "", "", "2023-12-16 14:53:22", "2023-12-16 07:53:22", "", "0", "http://comtim.vn/?p=292", "0", "post", "", "0");
