dng trong mi ba n hng ngy.</p>\n\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"451\" img_width=\"122\" pos=\"center\" class=\"icon-box-vsm icon-box-bl\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.1\"]\n\n<h3>S MNH</h3>\n<p class=\"mrb-0\">S mnh ca Cm Tm l cung cp nhng phn n b dng, mm ngon v an lnh. Chng ti cam kt mang n cho khch hng s la chn an ton v cht lng vi nhng mn n em li nng lng cn thit cho mt cuc sng khe mnh. ng thi, chng ti hng n vic to ra gii php khi nghip thnh cng thng qua m hnh nhng quyn hiu qu v chi ph u t thp, nhm to nn tng cho s pht trin bn vng ca cng ng v x hi.\n</p>\n\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"8\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"453\" img_width=\"122\" pos=\"center\" class=\"icon-box-vsm\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.1\"]\n\n<h3>GI TR CT LI</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Nguyn liu cht lng cao</strong>\n<p>Chng ti cam kt s dng nguyn liu ti ngon, c chn la k lng v p ng tiu chun cht lng cao nht.\n</p>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Sng to v a dng mn n</strong>\n<p>Chng ti khng ngng i mi v a dng ha cc mn n em n s la chn mi m v hp dn cho khch hng.</p>\n</li>\n<li><strong>i tc ng tin cy</strong>\n<p>Chng ti xy dng mi quan h ng tin cy vi i tc kinh doanh v i tc nhng quyn  m bo s pht trin bn vng v hp tc lu di. </p>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Lun i mi v hi nhp vi th trng</strong>\n<p>Chng ti khng ngng tm kim nhng xu hng mi  p ng nhu cu thay i ca th trng, ma	ng n s a dng cho sn phm.\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]", "Gii thiu", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "21-revision-v1", "", "", "2023-12-18 10:50:33", "2023-12-18 03:50:33", "", "21", "http://comtim.vn/?p=456", "0", "revision", "", "0");
