_size__sm=\"1\"]\n\n<h3>Sn phm cht lng</h3>\n<p>Ti Cm Tm, cht lng l tn ch ct li. Chng ti m bo ngun nguyn liu ti ngon, c nhp vi gi gc t nh my sn xut.\n</p>\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"515\" img_width=\"114\" pos=\"center\" class=\"icon-box_choose\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.1\" font_size__sm=\"1\"]\n\n<h3>Li nhun hp dn - chi ph thp</h3>\n<p>Cng vi s cam kt v cht lng, Cm Tm ti u chi ph tt nht cho ngun hng (vi cht lng cao) v gim thiu hao ht trong qu trnh vn hnh  to li nhun cao hn.</p>\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"517\" img_width=\"114\" pos=\"center\" class=\"icon-box_choose\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.1\" font_size__sm=\"1\"]\n\n<h3>H tr truyn thng</h3>\n<p>Khi ng hnh cng Cm Tm, bn s c chia s cc chng trnh Marketing chung ca thng hiu, c truyn thng Marketing, truyn thng bn hng v ln k hoch pht trin ring cho m hnh hp tc ca bn.</p>\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"518\" img_width=\"114\" pos=\"center\" class=\"icon-box_choose\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.1\" font_size__sm=\"1\"]\n\n<h3>H tr setup - khai trng - vn hnh</h3>\n<p>Chng ti h tr bn trong qu trnh setup ban u, chun b ton b dng c, hng dn v  xut chng trnh khuyn mi  c th khai trng sun s, vn hnh ng cch.</p>\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"520\" img_width=\"114\" pos=\"center\" class=\"icon-box_choose\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.1\" font_size__sm=\"1\"]\n\n<h3>H tr o to chuyn nghip</h3>\n<p>o to l yu t quan trng trong vic thnh cng. Cm Tm cam kt o to nghip v bn hng, cch thc vn hnh v qun l chuyn nghip. Bn s c c hi tham gia cc chng trnh o to ca Cm tm, chia s cc b quyt  bn pht trin k nng v kin thc trong ngnh.\n</p>\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]\n[section bg_color=\"rgb(255, 246, 252)\" padding=\"80px\" padding__sm=\"40px\"]\n\n[row]\n\n[col span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.4\" font_size__sm=\"1.3\"]\n\n<h2 class=\"uppercase lts-04 fw-800 pd17 head_div\">M HNH HP TC NHNG QUYN LINH HOT</h2>\n\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\" depth=\"1\" depth_hover=\"2\"]\n\n[ux_banner height=\"75%\" bg=\"524\" bg_size=\"original\" hover=\"zoom\"]\n\n[text_box style=\"circle\" hover=\"fade-out\" width=\"36\" width__sm=\"50\" scale=\"95\" scale__sm=\"98\" padding=\"0px 0px 0px 0px\" position_x=\"50\" position_y=\"50\" bg=\"rgba(85, 29, 71, 0.884)\" depth=\"2\" depth_hover=\"3\"]\n\n<h3 class=\"uppercase\">M hnh xe lu ng</h3>\n\n\n[/text_box]\n\n[/ux_banner]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\" depth=\"1\" depth_hover=\"2\"]\n\n[ux_banner height=\"75%\" bg=\"525\" bg_size=\"original\" hover=\"zoom\"]\n\n[text_box style=\"circle\" hover=\"fade-out\" width=\"36\" width__sm=\"50\" scale=\"95\" scale__sm=\"98\" padding=\"0px 0px 0px 0px\" position_x=\"50\" position_y=\"50\" bg=\"rgba(85, 29, 71, 0.884)\" depth=\"2\" depth_hover=\"3\"]\n\n<h3 class=\"uppercase\">M hnh c nh</h3>\n\n\n[/text_box]\n\n[/ux_banner]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]", "Nhng quyn", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "27-revision-v1", "", "", "2023-12-18 16:57:55", "2023-12-18 09:57:55", "", "27", "http://comtim.vn/?p=527", "0", "revision", "", "0");
