 img=\"443\" img_width=\"107\" pos=\"right\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.1\" font_size__sm=\"1\"]\n\n<h3>Tri nghim m thc ngon ming</h3>\r\nTo ra nhng ba n vi hng v tuyt vi  khch hng c th thng thc nhng ba n ngon hng ngy.\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\" animate=\"fadeInRight\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"444\" img_width=\"107\" pos=\"left\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.1\" font_size__sm=\"1\"]\n\n<h3>An ton v dinh dng</h3>\r\nTun th nghim ngt cc tiu chun v an ton thc phm, m bo rng mi khu phn n u an ton, b dng v lnh mnh.\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\" animate=\"fadeInLeft\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"445\" img_width=\"107\" pos=\"right\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.1\" font_size__sm=\"1\"]\n\n<h3>Tin li cho cuc sng bn rn</h3>\r\nMang n s tin li, p ng nhu cu khch hng c th tn hng ba n ngon m khng lo lng v vic chun b.\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\" animate=\"fadeInRight\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"446\" img_width=\"107\" pos=\"left\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.1\" font_size__sm=\"1\"]\n\n<h3>Cht lng v quy trnh bi bn</h3>\r\nTp trung vo vic duy tr cht lng v quy trnh sn xut bi bn  m bo s pht trin bn vng v s hi lng ca khch hng.\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]\n[section bg=\"347\" bg_size=\"original\" bg_overlay=\"rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.756)\" bg_pos=\"48% 68%\" parallax=\"7\" padding=\"79px\"]\n\n[row h_align=\"center\"]\n\n[col span=\"7\" span__sm=\"12\" padding__sm=\"0px 50px 0px 15px\" animate=\"fadeInLeft\" class=\"pd-0\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.3\" text_align=\"center\" text_color=\"rgb(255,255,255)\"]\n\n<h3>ng k ngay  nhn thng tin nhng quyn thng hiu</h3>\n[/ux_text]\n[contact-form-7 id=\"349\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]\n[section bg_color=\"rgb(255, 246, 252)\" padding=\"80px\"]\n\n[row]\n\n[col span__sm=\"12\" animate=\"fadeInLeft\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.4\" font_size__sm=\"1.3\"]\n\n<h2 class=\"uppercase lts-04 fw-800 pd17 head_div\">Tm nhn - s mnh - gi tr ct li</h2>\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[row h_align=\"center\"]\n\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\" animate=\"fadeInLeft\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"452\" img_width=\"122\" pos=\"center\" class=\"icon-box-vsm icon-box-bl\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.1\" font_size__sm=\"1\"]\n\n<h3>TM NHN</h3>\r\n<p class=\"mrb-0\">Tm nhn ca Cm Tm l tr thnh mt thng hiu hng u trong lnh vc m thc b dng v lnh mnh ti Vit Nam. Chng ti hng n vic cho khch hng nhng tri nghim tuyt vi v y  dinh dng trong mi ba n hng ngy.</p>\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\" animate=\"fadeInRight\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"451\" img_width=\"122\" pos=\"center\" class=\"icon-box-vsm icon-box-bl\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.1\" font_size__sm=\"1\"]\n\n<h3>S MNH</h3>\r\n<p class=\"mrb-0\">S mnh ca Cm Tm l cung cp nhng phn n b dng, mm ngon v an lnh. Chng ti cam kt mang n cho khch hng s la chn an ton v cht lng vi nhng mn n em li nng lng cn thit cho mt cuc sng khe mnh. ng thi, chng ti hng n vic to ra gii php khi nghip thnh cng thng qua m hnh nhng quyn hiu qu v chi ph u t thp, nhm to nn tng cho s pht trin bn vng ca cng ng v x hi.\r\n</p>\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"8\" span__sm=\"12\" animate=\"fadeInUp\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"453\" img_width=\"122\" pos=\"center\" class=\"icon-box-vsm\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.1\" font_size__sm=\"1\"]\n\n<h3>GI TR CT LI</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Nguyn liu cht lng cao</strong>\r\n<p>Chng ti cam kt s dng nguyn liu ti ngon, c chn la k lng v p ng tiu chun cht lng cao nht.\r\n</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>Sng to v a dng mn n</strong>\r\n<p>Chng ti khng ngng i mi v a dng ha cc mn n em n s la chn mi m v hp dn cho khch hng.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>i tc ng tin cy</strong>\r\n<p>Chng ti xy dng mi quan h ng tin cy vi i tc kinh doanh v i tc nhng quyn  m bo s pht trin bn vng v hp tc lu di. </p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>Lun i mi v hi nhp vi th trng</strong>\r\n<p>Chng ti khng ngng tm kim nhng xu hng mi  p ng nhu cu thay i ca th trng, ma	ng n s a dng cho sn phm.\r\n</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]\n[section bg_color=\"rgb(255, 246, 252)\" padding=\"0px\"]\n\n[row]\n\n[col span__sm=\"12\" animate=\"fadeInLeft\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.4\" font_size__sm=\"1.3\"]\n\n<h2 class=\"uppercase lts-04 fw-800 pd17 head_div\">i tc ca cm tm</h2>\n[/ux_text]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[row]\n\n[col span__sm=\"12\" animate=\"fadeInLeft\" class=\"pd-0\"]\n\n[ux_slider style=\"focus\" slide_width=\"500px\" arrows=\"false\" bullets=\"false\" timer=\"2000\" pause_hover=\"false\"]\n\n[row_inner]\n\n[col_inner span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"722\" image_size=\"original\" lightbox=\"true\" lightbox_image_size=\"original\" image_hover=\"zoom\"]\n\n\n[/col_inner]\n\n[/row_inner]\n[row_inner]\n\n[col_inner span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"720\" image_size=\"original\" lightbox=\"true\" lightbox_image_size=\"original\" image_hover=\"zoom\"]\n\n\n[/col_inner]\n\n[/row_inner]\n[row_inner]\n\n[col_inner span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"721\" image_size=\"original\" lightbox=\"true\" lightbox_image_size=\"original\" image_hover=\"zoom\"]\n\n\n[/col_inner]\n\n[/row_inner]\n\n[/ux_slider]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]", "Gii thiu", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "21-revision-v1", "", "", "2023-12-22 15:01:57", "2023-12-22 08:01:57", "", "21", "http://comtim.vn/?p=724", "0", "revision", "", "0");
