\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">c o to, hng dn cng vic;</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cp pht ng phc (ng phc, gi , thng ch sn phm...);</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C thm nhiu c hi pht trin, ng hnh cng MsSlim.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><b>4. Yu cu dnh cho ng vin:</b></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C xe my,  tui t 18-35 tui;</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Yu thch cng vic bn hng;</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ng gi, c trch nhim vi cng vic;</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nhanh nhn, trung thc, vui v;</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Giao tip lu lot;</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C kinh nghim bn hng l 1 li th.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">CV &amp; Portfolio gi v email: <a href=\"mailto:comtim.vn@gmail.com\"><strong>comtim.vn@gmail.com</strong></a></span></i>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lin h </span></i><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ms. Tho:</span></i><a href=\"tel:0363637611\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> 036 3637 611</span></i></a>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thng tin tham kho sn phm:</span></i>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/comtim.vn\">Fb.com/comtim.vn</a>", "Tuyn dng nhn vin bn hng", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "730-revision-v1", "", "", "2024-01-02 15:16:56", "2024-01-02 08:16:56", "", "730", "http://comtim.vn/?p=733", "0", "revision", "", "0");
